text: Saysomphone Phomvihane (; born 12 December 1954 in Houaphanh Province) is a Laotian politician and member of the Lao People's Revolutionary Party (LPRP). In 2021, he became the President of the National Assembly.Vietnamese National Assembly Chairman meets top Lao leader ==References== Category:Living people Category:1954 births Category:Presidents of the National Assembly (Laos)
title: Saysomphone Phomvihane
